Think of generation like this:
	•	Early tokens = choosing a valley
	•	Later tokens = rolling downhill within that valley

Your prompt created many viable valleys:
	•	systems theory
	•	philosophy
	•	analogy-heavy explanation
	•	critique

The model selected one and then stayed coherent within it.

